STATE
v.
Edward Charles GREEN 94P17-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 3, 2017 Edward Charles Green, for Green, Edward Charles. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, Maureen Krueger, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 21st of March 2017 by Defendant for Voter Fraud Dismissal:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 3rd of May 2017."
